OL,3,CEducation Minister says resolving
OL,4,Cindustrial action by teachers 'is a
OL,5,Cpriority'
OL,7,FTeachers and support staff should be
OL,8,Frecognised for the job they do,
OL,9,FStormont Education Minister Paul Givan
OL,10,Fhas said as he pledged to seek a
OL,11,Fresolution to industrial action.
OL,13,FEducation staff were among public
OL,14,Fsector workers who took part last
OL,15,Fmonth in the largest strike seen in
OL,16,Frecent history in Northern Ireland,
OL,17,Fcalling for pay parity with their
OL,18,Fcolleagues in the rest of the UK.
