OL,3,CEducation Minister says resolving
OL,4,Cindustrial action by teachers 'is a
OL,5,Cpriority'
OL,7,FThere has also been long-running
OL,8,Findustrial action short of a strike by
OL,9,Fteachers over conditions.
OL,11,FMr Givan is set to meet teacher unions
OL,12,Fnext week.
OL,14,FSpeaking during his first official
OL,15,Fvisit in the role, which was to
OL,16,FRathmore Grammar School in Belfast, Mr
OL,17,FGivan said resolving the industrial
OL,18,Faction is a priority for him.
OL,1,Wj5k7j5                          G2/10
