OL,3,CEducation Minister says resolving
OL,4,Cindustrial action by teachers 'is a
OL,5,Cpriority'
OL,7,F"The unions' desire to support their
OL,8,Fmembers, whether they are teachers or
OL,9,Fsupport staff, is the same desire that
OL,10,FI have. They should be recognised for
OL,11,Fthe job that they do," he said.
OL,13,F"We have superb teachers in Northern
OL,14,FIreland and that has to be reflected
OL,15,Fin the terms and conditions that they
OL,16,Fhave.
