OL,7,FThere was surprise in some quarters
OL,8,Fwhen the DUP choose the education
OL,9,Fbrief in their first pick of the
OL,10,Fministerial portfolios on Saturday
OL,11,Finstead of finance.
OL,13,FSinn Fein then nominated Caoimhe
OL,14,FArchibald to serve as Finance Minister.
OL,16,FMr Givan said he was delighted when
OL,17,FDUP leader Sir Jeffrey Donaldson asked
OL,18,Fhim to take on the role.
