OL,3,CEducation Minister says resolving
OL,4,Cindustrial action by teachers 'is a
OL,5,Cpriority'
OL,7,F"We've got 350,000 children and young
OL,8,Fpeople within our education system,
OL,9,Fthat's the future and I have a huge
OL,10,Fresponsibility to make sure they get
OL,11,Fthe education which they need to
OL,12,Ffulfil their potential, and that means
OL,13,Fsupporting teachers, our schools and
OL,14,FI'm going to do that in terms of the
OL,15,Fambition that I have and the asks that
OL,16,FI'm going to be making to the
OL,17,FExecutive to allow me to do the job."
OL,19,FMr Givan said discussions within the
OL,20,FExecutive on budget allocations for
OL,21,Fdepartments are ongoing.
