OL,7,F"Education is something that cuts
OL,8,Facross political boundaries and I am
OL,9,Fconfident that a Sinn Fein Finance
OL,10,FMinister will recognise the importance
OL,11,Fof education, and my Executive
OL,12,Fcolleagues will recognise that we need
OL,13,Fto invest in our capital estate and in
OL,14,Four teachers, and so whenever the ask
OL,15,Fcomes I am hopeful that they will
OL,16,Frespond positively to all of that," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
