OL,7,F"The Executive does have constraints
OL,8,Fin terms of the financial envelope
OL,9,Fthat is available to it. We have
OL,10,Fpressures in every department. My job
OL,11,Fis to advocate for the Department of
OL,12,FEducation and I will be a champion for
OL,13,Fmy department and for getting the
OL,14,Fresources that we need to deliver that
OL,15,Fworld-class education system in
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland."
